{"tid":903621,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭外海發現8公尺的蟲！ 潛水客大驚","createTime":"2018-11-15T16:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T12:32:20.000Z","uid":16864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"adad1787687408da21ece29add7c319d463f6bf0","tid":903621,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/201811141210139591_58064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F201811141210139591_58064.jpg&h=1d5ce4ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=46GtJJorxIg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D46GtJJorxIg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=w6KT%2BKEW50acgijZ%2FDEmhcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=8e6946c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=46GtJJorxIg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n56歲的哈撒韋（Steve Hathaway）和48歲的巴特爾（Andrew Buttle）最近在紐西蘭火山島「白島」外海潛水，發現一條逾8公尺長的蟲。<br />\n<br />\n哈撒韋和的巴特爾10月到白島潛水。這條果凍狀的蟲在海中優雅游動，兩人試圖不干擾輕輕從旁游過時，牠偶爾會震動和鼓動。<br />\n<br />\n在水下約32英呎，這隻有機物緩慢悠遊約656英呎，不斷變換牠的形狀和大小。<br />\n<br />\n巴特爾表示：「我之前從未親眼見過牠，甚至影片或照片上也沒看過，我對這種生物的存在感到興奮又難以置信。」<br />\n<br />\n他說：「這個島距離主島48公里，海水中有大量魚群和營養物，可能營造了恰當條件，讓這條蟲長到這麼大。我想這可能是火體蟲（pyrosome），牠們偶爾會被漁網困住，但就我所知沒有很多完整的大型樣本。」<br />\n<br />\n哈撒韋創辦教育娛樂平台「年輕海洋探險家」（Young Ocean Explorers）鼓勵孩童探索海洋，他表示：「毫無疑問，這趟旅行的重點就是尋找火體蟲，這麼多年來我一直想親眼看到。」"},{"pid":"599bb07df2180eba36497881a8fc77b321898be8","tid":903621,"uid":25955,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"成個巨型condom咁"},{"pid":"0f2c633e241d3bd317439ff25bd61b648c1fbdd5","tid":903621,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:37:05.000Z","msg":"幾百萬條連成一線"},{"pid":"9ce6bb14528f03a283ece727eb9b6579f921c17d","tid":903621,"uid":37912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T19:41:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7823fd6efa4f771ea05918fc5e7706584402513c","tid":903621,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"係一條蟲，定好多條一齊？"},{"pid":"60dda0cfd7471e857874a2c69b410c6f97ef5189","tid":903621,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7823fd6efa4f771ea05918fc5e7706584402513c","tid":903621,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"係一條蟲，定好多條一齊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"應該係一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1600af0b7f20089bb216746025332d7a8e42ac","tid":903621,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"有更多圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-6379797/Divers-capture-huge-deep-sea-worm-measuring-26-feet-long.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsciencetech%2Farticle-6379797%2FDivers-capture-huge-deep-sea-worm-measuring-26-feet-long.html&d=w6KT%2BKEW50acgijZ%2FDEmhcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7ae4e025\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-6379797/Divers-capture-huge-deep-sea-worm-measuring-26-feet-long.html</a>"},{"pid":"e43b85c5dbfbd07b8d1c479c3ae3aca8cc474619","tid":903621,"uid":47172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60dda0cfd7471e857874a2c69b410c6f97ef5189","tid":903621,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7823fd6efa4f771ea05918fc5e7706584402513c","tid":903621,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"係一條蟲，定好多條一齊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"應該係一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"火體蟲群體是由幾百到幾千個被稱為&quot;個蟲&quot;的個體組成的圓筒形或錐形群體，其尺寸範圍從小於一厘米到幾米長。他們通常被稱為&quot;海泡菜&quot;。<br />\n每個「個蟲」只有幾毫米大小"},{"pid":"bf9b6c56cd3a9335722ffff6f8f366bfe5a7718d","tid":903621,"uid":37445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"應該幾鮮味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}